CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 27, 1952, pg. 15 reads: "Club Woman Honored -Mrs. Margaret McDaniels was given a testimonial reception last Wednesday night in Centre Avenue YWCA by a  group of friends and admirers.  In the picture are: Mrs. Nannie B. Allen, Mrs. Martha Tyson, Mrs. Lena Wims, Mrs. Anna Mae Nixon, Mrs. Gertrude Ward, Mrs. Lillian Thompson, Mrs. Ruth David, Mrs. Mary White, Mrs. Hattie Worthy, Mrs. Lelia Payne, Mrs. Mammie Koger, Mrs. Anessesa Poindexter, Mrs. Peggy Price Freeman, and in the center, Mr. and Mrs. Emmett McDaniels. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Emmett McDanieI, seated center, in front of thirteen women, including: Nannie B. Allen, Martha Tyson, Lena Wims, Anna Mae Nixon, Gertrude Ward, Lillian Thompson, Ruth David, Mary White, Hattie Worthy, Lelia Payne, Mammie Koger, Anessesa Poindexter, and Peggy Price Freeman, posed in Centre Avenue YWCA for testimonial reception
